        <header>Conforming amendments</header>
				<paragraph commented="no" id="H6321E1E3ADFA44CC8265D311FB95EFA2">
          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <text>
            <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:1016/ss:a">
              <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/26/1016">Section 1016(a)</external-xref> of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986</cato:entity-ref> is amended by striking <quote>and</quote> at the end of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:1016/ss:a/p:36">paragraph (36)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking the period at the end of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:1016/ss:a/p:37">paragraph (37)</cato:entity-ref> and inserting <quote>, and</quote>, and by inserting after <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:1016/ss:a/p:37">paragraph (37)</cato:entity-ref> the following new paragraph:</text>
					<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H94E08D05333D4F0787A6CA0845727D07" style="OLC">
						<paragraph commented="no" id="H5B06B97D53B74B23B6D59391832C825C">
              <enum>(38)</enum>
              <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">to the extent provided in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:h/p:2" proposed="true">section 30E(h)(2)</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
            </paragraph>
            <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
          </quoted-block>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="HA9230AA021044B5ABA72825BFAEA64AD">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text>The table of sections for <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:B">subpart B of part IV of subchapter A of chapter 1 of the Internal Revenue
			 Code of 1986</cato:entity-ref> is amended by adding at the end the following new item:</text>
					<quoted-block id="H49EC193508FE4F85BD614B956D216537" style="OLC">
						<toc>
							<toc-entry idref="H4183004D6AC44F63803A3B923A47F3D5" level="section">Sec. 30E. Angel investment tax credit.</toc-entry>
            </toc>
