      </subsection>
      <subsection id="H9EA12656126540F3942FC42BF8A22661">
        <enum>(d)</enum>
        <header>Effective date</header>
        <text>The amendments made by this section shall apply to investments made after December 31, 2013, in
			 taxable years ending after such date.</text>
			</subsection>
    </section>
